    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税生效远足贸易征税至100年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-tariffs-take-effect-hiking-trade-levies-to-a-100-year-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的所谓互惠关税现已达到现实，在他推动巨大重新订购全球贸易的努力时，对世界经济造成了雷鸣般的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-tariffs-take-effect-hiking-trade-levies-to-a-100-year-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，药品征收“很快”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-says-long-promised-pharmaceutical-tariffs-due-very-shortly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，他对药品的长期征收的关税即将到来，这是他计划在全球征税的市场后退的最新信号，他计划向更高的部门关税提前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/trump-says-long-promised-pharmaceutical-tariffs-due-very-shortly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 02:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
